Vote_embed.title: Session Vote
Vote_embed.description: Our management team has decided to start a session poll. If you are able to attend the session please click the 'Vote' button below. You are required to join after you vote or you will be punished.

second_part_embed.title: Requirements
second_part_embed.description:
You are required to join our server within 15 minutes of it starting.
You are required to read our in game rules before joining.

Votes_view_embed.title: Session Votes
Votes_view_embed.description: These are the list of people who have voted for the session. Note that you are able to remove your vote by clicking the vote button again.

added.description: Your session vote has been added.

removed.description: Your session vote has been removed.
